name: '3AM' on 7" Vinyl
description:
Delivery date will be Monday 4th October 2010.
A digital download voucher is included.
All copies are signed by KMKM.

This is our first release on 'Stone Door Records' and includes the B-side 'I Dance You Dance.' Both tracks were record on location at The Hyde Park Picture House, Leeds. The beautiful 100 year old cinema sounded just as good as she looked!

www.myspace.com/kissmekillmeofficial

name: Launch night tickets
description:
Location: Main Room @ The Cockpit, Leeds
(650 capacity)

Tickets to our launch night in Feb 2010. Expect a well known support band and an up and coming local band to open the night. Music will come a very special guest DJ.

The ticket price includes a wristband to attend the HMV launch and aftershow party. Also includes a signed photo of the band.

Postage and packaging included
